title: Can A Virgin Harlem Shake & Body Roll?
itunes:title: Can A Virgin Harlem Shake & Body Roll?
description:
FRI 11/18 - Yvonne Orji aka Molly from HBO's "Insecure" stops by The Breakfast Club to talk about the show, her Nigerian upbringing, why she still has her virginity, how she got her start in comedy & acting. The legendary Sinbad also kicks it with Envy, Angela & Charlamagne to give his comedic take on the election and world events. Then an indecisive hee-haw almost goes to Kanye West...or does it?
